WEBVTT

02:51.571 --> 02:53.339
Hey, that job was to be
a good grandpa,

02:53.406 --> 02:54.741
I-I go
where the kid goes.

02:54.841 --> 02:56.176
Don't touch me!

02:56.242 --> 02:58.144
How long have I --
you said you weren't a robot!

02:58.211 --> 02:59.746
It killed me to lie to you,
Morty.

02:59.846 --> 03:02.048
But it would have literally
killed me not to lie to you.
